    <h1 itemprop="headline" class=" ">Donald Trump promises &#039;historic&#039; increase in US military budget</h1>

    
            <div class="intro">
                <p>Upcoming budget will ask for $54bn increase in US defence budget</p>
      </div>
            <ul class="caption meta inline-pipes-list">
              <li class="author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
          <span itemprop="name"><a href="/author/samuel-osborne" title="Samuel Osborne" itemprop="sameAs">Samuel Osborne</a></span>
                  </li>
                    <li>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/SamuelOsborne93">@SamuelOsborne93</a>
        </li>
                    <li title="27 February 2017 15:01 London"><time data-microtimes='{"published":"1488207660000","display":0,"changed":"1488207660000"}' datetime="Mon, 02/27/2017 - 15:01">Monday 27 February 2017 15:01 GMT</time></li>
                    <li class="comments">
          <a href="#commentsDiv" id="comment-count" class="icon-comment"></a>
        </li>
          </ul>
